{"tid":1778551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（記得做埋洗版任務）施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2019-12-11T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T14:33:20.000Z","uid":54870,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a626273636f7139d99541a4909436771abed100a","tid":1778551,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"be54b10086a26498775aacab2cf1c06abcc30b53","tid":1778551,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"【抵制CCTVB每日任務】<br />\n😡1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 🙅🏻&zwj;♀️3.罷買 👍🏻4.互Like留言<br />\n<br />\n是日精選@11/12<br />\n💎 House730 💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/house730/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fhouse730%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=435dcbc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/house730/</a><br />\n👆去派嬲兼留言👆<br />\n<br />\n#House730<br />\n<br />\n老細係施永青，奶共界KOL 🇨🇳👏🏻<br />\n<br />\n連出2篇社論，批評「黃色經濟圈」<br />\n驚驚豬喔？😂<br />\n<br />\n重點摘錄 ✏️<br />\n「市場機制的基本要素，是可以透過消費者的自由選擇來汰弱留強」<br />\n「作為生意人⋯⋯當然想做整個社會的生意」<br />\n「商界希望黃絲高抬貴手」<br />\n<br />\n多謝提點！ 黃絲一定不會高抬貴手😆<br />\n揾樓可以幫趁 <a href=\"http://www.squarefoot.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.squarefoot.com.hk&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=dfe50e4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.squarefoot.com.hk</a> ✅<br />\n<br />\n👁 更多: TVB廣告客戶名單<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JSJaQK&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=8f3f71c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JSJaQK</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n🏃🏻&zwj;♂👉請即follow:<br />\nInstagram: @sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=bec0bb1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=eebb8c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"3b4ebfce4cfc81f128d7beea3660e18454a3bdfb","tid":1778551,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"抵制CCTVB<br />\n人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77322ae77fa02cc1d246aaade57bd009743f55fd","tid":1778551,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:51:27.000Z","msg":"抵制cctvb"},{"pid":"d13baf600b1b8d51ee1048d4e5d55eb4fe723d74","tid":1778551,"uid":254450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"施生聖誕快樂，今年準備好聖誕卡未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37baf784c2c81df3373b2561c570986e69b54cd","tid":1778551,"uid":174639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"方丈好撚小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b3e094a779478cd9fdaff82996631097a66735","tid":1778551,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐聖誕卡都唔知咩嚟<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2292e90d3818e8fc8a700d2efdd87303db9b20de","tid":1778551,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":